{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "共融", "storyInfo": "拉特蘭之外，產生了“墮天”症狀的薩科塔們紛紛啟程返回拉特蘭。費德里科與阿爾圖羅脫離“夢境”，拉特蘭城內異象頻生。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g2_kazdelstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你趕著投胎啊？走這麼快！我們抬的是一塊源石結晶板啊，等一下摔壞就都死翹翹了。", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這家人也真是的，用這種東西壓泡菜，也不怕吃進嘴裡的都是源石顆粒！", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別*薩卡茲粗口*囉囉嗦嗦了，快點。", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天之內清理完這個城區，這個任務不簡單，你也不想老大被那個老巫妖罵得臭血淋頭後再把我們罵得臭血淋頭吧。", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多間屋子，要把沾到源石的地方都清理乾淨……巴別塔都組建了專門的城建隊，為什麼不乾脆把它們推倒了重蓋？", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說回來，想到接下來哪裡都看不見源石，還真的有點不適應。", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉上你那張臭嘴。", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前是沒辦法，只有靠著礦脈的產出才能過活，現在卡茲戴爾已經不用再為能源苦惱了，當然要把屋子打掃乾淨……", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還真喜歡住在源石窩裡啊——喂，巫妖，看路！", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖，收好你的線頭，鬼知道你們那些線和源石打結之後，會惹出什麼麻煩……", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣說話很不禮貌哦。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是纏住了，就用你們的角幫我勾斷吧。不過那樣的話，我的絲弦會不會把你們拖進別的空間裡去呢？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薩卡茲工人們"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，不嚇你們了。先生們，請過去吧~", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#4$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，是我眼花了嗎？剛剛的光線是怎麼回事？", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面的房子？過去看看。", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……讓我去吧。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "薩卡茲工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那排房子緊貼著剛整合完畢的農田地塊，剛剛的光，應該是監測土壤的信標感應到了你們兩個搬的源石結晶板。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是維什戴爾知道這兩年好不容易開墾的農田被污染……", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧走吧。", "name": "薩卡茲工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_933_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g1_kazdelroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_352_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不要再往前了！", "name": "塞西莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#3$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$2"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃芒加德看著面前緊張的小女孩，她嘗試用自己小小的身軀擋住來人的視線。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩身後，薩科塔男性脫力般跪在地板上，他的光環與光翼支離破碎，那些碎片像是活物般顫抖著，忽明忽暗，彷彿故障的燈。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而薩科塔本人如同墮入了深深的夢中，不發一言。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是誰？你是來抓我們的嗎？", "name": "塞西莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小女孩很緊張，埃芒加德彎下腰，用手撐著膝蓋，儘量讓自己看起來沒有敵意，她甚至搖了搖自己充盈著能量的大尾巴。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可愛的小妹妹，我沒有惡意。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛應該聽到了，我支開了其他的薩卡茲。或許我能幫你們……幫他。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "塞西莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃芒加德關緊了身後的門，將可能的視線隔絕在外。"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_4", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她將自己的帽子扶正，看不見的絲弦逶迤向不可知的空間。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "49_g1_kazdelroom", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然高塔上那些繁文縟節和廢話連篇的經卷真的倒人胃口，但對比現在，我真的得向那對雙子羊鞠躬，感謝她們的禮遇。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰受得了每項政策都只能口頭傳達而且動不動還得翻來覆去解釋好幾遍，什麼時候才能對我們的公務員進行普及教育……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急事。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……說。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在節點爐這邊發現了兩個光環破碎的薩科塔……其中一個狀態非常非常，不對勁。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶他們回來，儘量別讓其他人注意到，免得引起騷亂。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去把維什戴爾踹醒。到了需要這個議長主持緊急會議的時候了。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "49_g1_kazdelroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g6_towerterrace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真是一份很長的名單啊。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，就職於崔林特爾梅各個高塔的四十三名薩科塔，未經任何允許，全部擅自脫離了自己的崗位。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，伊維格娜德。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們硬是突破了厄登赫爾大區入境檢查的哨站，已經離開了萊塔尼亞。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞無私地收容了這些離群者，然而他們如今卻選擇叛逃了……毫無徵兆。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也不能說毫無徵兆。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帝國音樂學院的守夜人目擊到一位薩科塔學者離開了，他的光環和光翼都已經破碎……像是發生了很嚴重的意外。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墮天？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#4$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不完全像。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認為應該如何處理呢？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您——您在問我的意見？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾·沃爾夫岡，你現在是“無情權威”的代言人。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了我以外，你是她留在世間唯一的聲音。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和幾年前比起來，你的個子長高了一些，心境成長了不少，希爾德加德把你教得很好。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你今天能站在這裡向我彙報所有的情報，值得讚譽。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#11$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這代表你向我坦白了自己有一些特別的管道。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞的薩科塔集體“墮天”並叛逃，茲事體大……伊維格娜德，您是唯一有能力處理此事的人。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為獎勵，我也不介意你、烏提卡的那個孩子，甚至那個小伯爵私底下的一些動作。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，讓我們言歸正傳。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "入境檢查隊的報告中說，他們離去的方向，應該是拉特蘭。這次叛逃事件極可能有拉特蘭官方參與其中。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是否需要派遣女皇之聲，向教皇廳討個說法？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一年前，伊萬杰利斯塔十一世曾在女皇慶典之後與我聯絡，他請求與萊塔尼亞攜手並進。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這群薩科塔如今的種種異常，或許說明，那場讓教宗深為忌憚、不得不主動向我們尋求幫助的“災異”，已經降臨了。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向所有高塔發出詔令，召集最優秀的術師與學者……以“永恆恩典”與“無情權威”共同的名義。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災難不會對這片大地的任何一處留私，我們需要儘快解讀那自混沌中取來的秘密。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我馬上去安排。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒不用這麼急。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#9$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我的意思是，我去知會女皇之聲，讓她們去……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾，今天的晚霞也很美麗啊，陪我看看吧。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空的傷口早已癒合……她也會喜歡現在的夜晚，對吧？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#11$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_campsite_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……拉烏尼達東邊的東邊，白色的聖城，拉特蘭♪", "name": "帳篷裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡的銃炮放出煙火，那裡的靶子都是蘋果♪", "name": "帳篷裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我們誠心祈禱，祂便給予麵包♪", "name": "帳篷裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我們向祂奔去，祂便賜予救贖♪", "name": "帳篷裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唱吧，唱到睡著。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們夢裡的神可是比拉特蘭的主還要仁慈。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守夜不需要跑這麼遠，奧羅拉。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……滾開。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡已經是米諾斯的地界，辛嘉斯的那幫貴族佬不會再追過來，你們安全了。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修道院已經不復存在了，各奔東西吧。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前，你一聲不吭地來到我的修道院，幫我把地塊從那幫貴族手裡保下來，如今你要離開，又是一聲不吭。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你佈你的道，我幫你保護那些孩子，換個落腳的地方，順便而已。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把自己看得太重要了。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉……你不能離開。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉，我不是在請求你。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們接下來的目的地相同，我們會與你結伴而行，一同前往拉特蘭。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我什麼時候說過，回拉特蘭要帶著你們？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在一起十年了，奧羅拉。對羽蛇來說，這是很長很長的一段時光。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我或許確實沒有那麼相信拉特蘭，但我總該相信你。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭剝奪了你的公民身分，你無數次在我唱詩時咒罵那座城市……", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但看看你自己，哪怕你已經在玻利瓦爾待了那麼久，卻還是不肯脫下這套銃騎的甲胄……", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕你已經成為墮天使，無法再使用守護銃，卻依然想盡辦法取得了這架黑鋼的銃械，你從來都沒有——", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#10$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_bigaxe_d", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墮天使突然將武器往前送，漆黑的銃管幾乎抵在了羽蛇的唇邊。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是相信我，就該記得我告訴過你很多次，那座聖城沒那麼友愛，沒那麼仁慈和寬容……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從修道院跟著你走到這裡的人，有一半都不是薩科塔。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開玻利瓦爾後，你們有的是活路可找。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們信的或許不是拉特蘭真正的教條，但我們是憑著這個信仰，才得以在玻利瓦爾那樣混亂的地方勉強維持住還算有序的生活。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法說服大家離開玻利瓦爾後，不去朝聖……而是去其他地方。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同樣，我也沒辦法說服我自己。歷經漫長的歲月，拉特蘭已經是我們的一部分了。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在講笑話嗎……？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想想修道院裡的薩科塔，他們不在拉特蘭長大，莫名其妙墮天後，身心受到重創……", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有回到拉特蘭，才能知道發生了什麼，才能消除他們的恐慌，治好他們的“病”。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#8$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們再同行最後一段路吧，奧羅拉。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#9$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "努艾達，我回拉特蘭，完全不是因為思鄉情切。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道嗎？十年前，也是在一座修道院，有個老頭對我說過類似的話，他曾代表拉特蘭將我驅逐，就因為一些可笑的過錯。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他渴望從我嘴裡聽到一些懺悔、一些祈求。他告訴我，如果能夠誠心懺悔，或許還有回去的機會……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你拒絕了？", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拒絕了。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座城市想必出了不小的事，我回去，是要趁亂報復的。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "努艾達抬頭迎上冰冷的銃管，將它貼在臉側。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我們不會妨礙你的。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#13$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是需要一個領路人，一個知曉前方路途、能判明方向的人。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#15$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個像你一樣的人。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#13$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處帳篷裡的唱詩聲漸弱，孩子們呼喚的聲音三三兩兩地響起。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉嗤笑一聲，將銃收起。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g9_catastrophicalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_act16side_01_intro", "key": "$m_bat_act16side_01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_halogrow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_halogrow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1792_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "育嬰聖堂在周圍的建築上塗抹出色彩，像是開啟了一扇扇門，頭頂光環的奇特生物從門後析出，一個接著一個降落至地面。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了那隻木攀獸的幼獸，這些傢伙，也得到了拉特蘭的賜福？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（激動地拍掌）", "name": "蒙恩的生物A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1792_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不安地搖晃）", "name": "蒙恩的生物B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1792_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠們匍匐在地，奮力向上搖晃著腦袋，似乎還不太適應頭頂的光環。牠們的喉頭發出低沉而有規律的聲響，連綴成一片，猶如禱告。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，真是混沌的心聲，難聽。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果基於某種暫不明確的原因，聖城中的所有人此前都深陷於某種巨大的群體性幻覺中……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼眼前的景象，是否代表，真實與虛幻的界限被模糊了，實際的災難正在入侵拉特蘭？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這比你我在帕維永中的經歷更加難以理解。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，有隻傢伙已經注意到我們了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sealangel", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（禱告聲）", "name": "蒙恩的生物A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們發出的雜音，似乎驚擾了牠們的儀式。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿是因為沒有聽見禱告聲，一隻蒙恩的生物扭頭看向了費德里科與阿爾圖羅。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠的光環閃爍，臃腫的身軀似乎也變得輕盈，以極快的速度向兩人靠近。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dogangel_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1792_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1792_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科舉起銃，但頭頂光環的生物對此視若無睹，牠們的禱告聲不曾有一刻停歇。"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "退後。這些物種的來歷與屬性尚不明確，別陷入包圍。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你會毫不猶豫地射擊。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，你說，這些傢伙算是你我的同胞嗎？如果你現在開火，是否會觸犯律法？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是玩笑，還是不合時宜的提問？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的守護銃早已遺失，而我不需要開火也能制伏這些生物。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠們是否被算作同胞，雖有查明的必要，但並不是目前的優先事項。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，有一個人能解開我們的所有困惑。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……教宗，伊萬杰利斯塔十一世。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sealangel", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1791_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 445, "prop"